<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="poemXX">
      <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>porippuṟap pūḻiṉ pōrval cēvaṉ</l>
<l>mēntōl kaḷainta tīṅkōḷ veḷḷeṭ</l>
<l>cuḷakiṭai yuṇaṅkaṟ cevvi koṇṭeṉa</l>
<l>vēṉiṟ kōṅkiṉ pūmpokuṭ ṭaṉṉa</l>
<l>kuṭantaiyañ ceviya kōṭṭeli yāṭṭak</l>
<l>kaliyār varakiṉ piṟaṅkupī ḷoḷikkum</l>
<l>vaṉpula vaippi ṉatuvē ceṉṟu</l>
<l>tiṉpaḻam pacīi.... ṉaṉō pāṇa</l>
<l>vāḷvaṭu viḷaṅkiya ceṉṉic</l>
<l>ceruveṅ kuruci lōmpu mūrē.</l>
</lg>
